      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in showroom-grade condition. This specimen has been curated to the highest standards, exhibiting flawless exterior surfaces and an interior that remains in an immaculate, untouched state. Every mechanical component operates with the absolute precision intended by the original manufacturer. For the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle represents the definitive benchmark of its class.",
